<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about" id="about"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="sec-tag">About the Shop</div>
      <p class="about-lead">A name Sagar trusts for <i>fine gents' tailoring</i> and quality fabric.</p>
      <div class="about-body">
        <p>Shashankh Tailor and Fabric brings together two things every well-dressed man needs — <b>good cloth and a good stitch</b>. From selecting the right fabric to taking careful measurements, every step is done with attention so the final garment fits you just right.</p>
        <p>Whether it's a sharp suit for an occasion, a traditional sherwani or kurta for a wedding, or everyday shirts and trousers, the work is finished neatly, on time, and at a fair price.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#services" style="margin-top:8px">See what we offer →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="about-photo reveal" data-slot="about">
